 Main changes from previous release
 ----------------------------------

  * I've   included   the  card.b(c|h|map)  files  for  to  replace  the
    cardres.b(c|h|map) files included with Hisoft Basic 2.

  * Minor (not relevant) changes at #?.b(c|h) files.

  * Included  an  "simple" example (source code and executable), checked
    succesfully  over  my Amiga 1200with PCCard Linksys WiFi:  shows the
    manufacturer   and   product   ID,   the   card's   type  and  their
    version/revision.   WARNING!  Don't remove the card when the program
    is running, because this will reset the system!

